      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SCARBOROUGH PEST (3) jumped from out wide and was game in defeat last start when a 0.8 lengths second (30.01) behind Death Adder at this track. Good beginner aided by a nice draw. Makes plenty of appeal. JENNY DUTTON (1) ran below best last time finishing fourth (35.12) over 600m at this track from Box 8. Has ability and can atone. MASCARA GIRL (2) has been hard to follow lately, running sixth (30.96) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at this track. Good beginner and aided by a handy draw. Expecting sharp improvement this line-up. BANANA LECLERC (4) missed the placings here most recently but can sneak into the finish with the right run.",
